// Orchestrator Activity — high-level progress view for user
// ============================================================================

/**
 * OrchestratorActivity — tracks overall task progress
 * 
 * This is the USER-FACING progress view. It shows:
 *   - Overall progress [N/M]
 *   - Current step with arrow →
